{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_10", "eventName": "破碎日冕", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "10-3", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "低下頭", "storyInfo": "阿米婭小隊抵達出入口岸，卻遭遇薩卡茲巡邏隊大肆搜查出城人員。引路人驚惶逃走，再次撞上蔓德拉帶領的深池士兵。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g2_inexport", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "9:09 A.M. 天氣/陰"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倫蒂尼姆，薩迪恩區，三零九號出入口"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 前面......就是入口了。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "你在擔心什麼？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line18"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 嗯......其實到目前為止都很順利......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ——除了一件事。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#20$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 博士，一直以來與您和凱爾希醫生聯絡的那位信使，她本來會在我們抵達附屬地塊之後，就立刻與我們聯繫。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#20$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#20$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我記得這項約定。;......;她會不會出事？", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line28", "option2": "line33", "option3": "line38"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line43"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我們都在等......但也只能被動等待。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我本以為會親眼見到她，或者至少收到某種形式的訊息。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line43"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 博士，眼下的情況，我也不能對其他幹員多說什麼。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我們已經到了這裡，就必須繼續往前走。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "3"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line43"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#18$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 聯絡不上，就沒有辦法確認。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#18$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 希望她沒有遇上什麼意外......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我們還是按原定計劃進城。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 唔，前面好多人，都是從城內的方向湧過來的......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g15_customs", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......我們真就這麼逃出來了？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這條路是安全的，我鄰居一家上周就是從這裡走的。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要能申請到出城證，士兵們就不會為難我們。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我......我其實不是這個意思。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道。我腦子裡的想法應該和你一樣。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "四年前，我頭一回見到薩卡茲的軍隊出現在新聞裡。那時候我並沒有多想。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 是啊，我也是。陛下離去之後，亂糟糟的事情總是不少，誰知道又有哪位大公爵心血來潮，將魔族也招攬進了軍隊裡呢？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩年前，我看見薩卡茲的軍隊走在特倫菲爾德區的街道上。那件事成了我在下班路上，與同事的談資。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我也記得......彷彿一夜之間，有些事情就悄悄變了。我們這些住在卡登區公爵辦事處附近的，看見這些變化，要更晚一些。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大半年前，薩卡茲的軍隊站在了我們銀行門口。他們帶走了我們行長，因為她的丈夫在城防軍中擔任要職。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 唉，在那之後，你是不是再也沒見過他們？在我們住的街區，警員們也都換了面孔，他們之中的好些個都長著那可怕的角。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再然後......昨天。我看到有薩卡茲來到我家對面的街角，他們在......挨家挨戶地敲門。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 所以你逃出來了？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實我的父母早就走了。我只是......我放不下這份銀行櫃員的收入。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 誰又不是呢。倫蒂尼姆......真離開了這座城市，我們就都回不去以前那種生活了吧？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是別說了。走吧，都走吧。比起賺錢，我更想活命。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g2_inexport", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 這裡每天都是這副樣子嗎？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......從某一天開始，大概就是如此。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 特雷西斯的軍隊......他們並不阻撓平民出城？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看起來，他並不在意讓倫蒂尼姆之外的人知曉現在倫蒂尼姆真正的掌權人是誰。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#10$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "外面那些大貴族不介意？;維多利亞議會的情況如何？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line118", "option2": "line131"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line138"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想，他們無疑時時刻刻都在關注倫蒂尼姆的動向。這正是他們在城外屯兵的原因。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他們更在意彼此的動作。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對有意入主倫蒂尼姆的各大公爵來說，無論誰率先對城內的薩卡茲發起進攻，都可能在這場持續了二十多年的競賽中占得先機。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們之中，有誰樂意看到本可能屬於自己的王座被別人捷足先登？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#6$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這種情況下，任意一位公爵表露出進攻的意向，都可能會被幾則通訊、一場聚會邀請和一系列的來自自己領地的不利消息打斷。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而若是他執意進軍，等待著他的一定是一場失利，這場失利甚至不需要耗費城內的薩卡茲攝政王一兵一卒。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line138"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我不知道。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們離開倫蒂尼姆的時候，那一天的倫蒂尼姆，與之前的任何一天都沒有太大不同。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，我曾經以為，只要議會仍在運作一天，倫蒂尼姆就並不會陷入真正的混亂。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於城內的具體情況，我們只有在進去之後才能看清楚了。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位，我已經把你們帶到這裡......剩下的路，你們就自己走了吧？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 沒問題。謝謝您，托馬斯先生，您幫了我們一個大忙。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#8$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#13$1"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 各小組注意，我們按之前的安排，分批混入面前的人流裡——", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#13$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 可露希爾小組先走，確定前路通暢之後，推進之王小組跟上。我與博士會殿後。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#13$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 偵察小組請持續留意周圍情況，如有異常，立刻通報。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#13$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 白輪，還是由你帶托馬斯先生從原路返......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#13$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 阿米婭！", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 請說。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 前方突發騷亂，看起來像是有薩卡茲士兵過來了！", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......！", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#20$1"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 全體注意，潛入行動中止，我們先就近隱蔽！", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#20$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g15_customs", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warchaos_intro", "key": "$warchaos_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"t