{"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說的就是你，不許走！", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 快點......再走快一點，我們馬上就能出......出城......", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 啊——！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是這個人。", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先、先生，您......您別打我，我願意跟您回去......我們是犯了什麼錯嗎？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愛滾哪去滾哪去，別站在這裡礙事。", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽好了，誰都不許動！", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都給我原地待著。你，你，還有你，把臉轉過來！", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你包裡裝什麼了？是不是武器？全倒出來看看！", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你臉上為什麼有灼傷？還挺新的......就是你，給我滾出隊列！", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你說做麵包的時候被燙傷了？你當我們是傻子嗎！", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘁......看樣子真不是被我們的武器弄的。我說，你不是反抗軍吧？", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嚇暈過去了。算了，這個先帶走。", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"channel": "bse", "volume": 0.3, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 中尉，我們走不了了。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是我的責任。送你們來這裡之前，我應該先注意下有沒有追兵。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#5$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 您千萬別這麼說。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不管是我們這幾個被深池抓住的兄弟，還是老湯姆他們那幾個被薩卡茲折磨更久的，我們在被你救出來之前，都已經與死人無異了。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 那滋味真的太絕望了......我寧可戰死沙場，而不是這麼窩囊又稀裡糊塗地就被敵人關了起來。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倫蒂尼姆的淪陷絕不是你們的錯。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 那更不可能是您的錯。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 是您把我們從絕望的境地裡拉了出來。至少，我能靠自己的雙腿走到這裡，我已經多活了一個小時。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我說我沒法再戰鬥下去了，您也沒有怪我，而是冒險把我們送到這裡。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 中尉，您走吧。只有您一個人的話，還來得及躲起來，躲開這些薩卡茲的視線，找個安全的地方藏好。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我們傷的傷病的病，只會連累您。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我絕不會拋下你們任何一個人。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哈......要是當時我的長官也能像您一樣，我們是不是......也不至於輸得這麼快這麼慘？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 見到您以後，我其實就意識到了，我也想像您一樣再做些什麼......", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是想......不，不可以！", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 您說，我們幾個老兄弟一塊衝過去，能帶走幾個薩卡茲？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......都給我聽好了。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰都不許行動。這是命令。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 命令......", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 好。您現在是我的長官了，我願意服從您的命令。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從這裡走到薩卡茲士兵所在的位置，還有幾分鐘。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "全部低下頭。記住我教你們的，你們都是來自附近街區的無業者，受的傷是為了搶一塊麵包而互毆留下的。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 薩卡茲......會信？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今的薩迪恩區一片亂象，他們自然也都見識過。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管他們信不信，就算逼問起來，你們也......暫時忍一忍。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬一有誰忍不住......", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我們明白。被薩卡茲發現的話，我們絕不牽連其他人。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬一誰忍不住，我會動手。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 中尉......？！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先靜觀其變。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"channel": "bse", "volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g2_inexport", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"channel": "bse", "volume": 0.3, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這邊沒有。", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那邊呢？那邊還有幾個，還有升降梯後面，那塊結構特別容易藏人！", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們幾個，過去仔細看看！", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 那些士兵看起來是在找人。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#15$1"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 各小組，彙報方位。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#15$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......位置確認完畢。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "他們不像在找我們。;我們應該還沒暴露。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line328", "option2": "line328"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我同意。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 博士，還記得我們出發前與凱爾希醫生一起做的情況推演吧？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#8$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 有一種可能性，我們在倫蒂尼姆與維多利亞各處活躍的秘密信使確實失敗了。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 他們沒有來得及傳來正確的情報，羅德島的全部動向都被特雷西斯掌握。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#18$1"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 那麼，只要我們一進入倫蒂尼姆，特雷西斯的親兵很可能就會站在我們面前。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#18$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 可是眼前的情況似乎不太一樣......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我以為等著我們的起碼是赦罪師。;......;我們不至於這麼沒面子吧？", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line344", "option2": "line344", "option3": "line344"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我和博士的判斷應該是一致的。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 特雷西斯目前還不知道我們已經到了。否則的話，我們很難一路走到這裡。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 那麼，眼前這些薩卡茲士兵，在搜捕的應該是其他恰好出現在這裡的人......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 欸，托馬斯先生......？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 阿米婭，他突然就想跑出去，我差點沒攔住！", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不要攔著我，我不能在這裡......", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#14$1"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 托馬斯先生，您最好不要擅自行動！這樣會非常危險！", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#14$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#15$1"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我答應過您，會讓幹員護送您離開，但很抱歉，我們當前還不能......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#15$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哎呦！", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 等、等等，您不能搶奪我們幹員的武器——！", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉了，我、我還不想死！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 這到底是怎麼回事......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "答案很明顯了。;他覺得士兵們在找他。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line379", "option2": "line379"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也不想這樣......我只是給薩卡茲開了半年車而已！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們占了我的煉糖廠，又逼我給他們運東西，我在城外的一家老小都還要活下去......我能怎麼辦？！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那天我就看了一眼，一小眼，我哪能猜到他們在用我的廠房做什麼......", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們一直追我，我知道一旦被追上，他們一定會殺了我！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們為什麼都要找我......我往哪裡跑都要沒命！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我不能坐以待斃......", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 托馬斯先生！", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 白輪！別追了，不能暴露自己。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "bse", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_desert_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"i